unittitle_ssm: New York University Archives Photographic Slides Collection
abstract_ssm: The New York University Archives Photographic Slides Collection was created by the University Archives to group together slides documenting New York University activities, schools and departments, staff, students, buildings, and classrooms.  Materials in the collection date from 1900 to 2002, with the bulk of the slides dating from the 1970s to 2002.
